page.title: 11Gweek Sports Club
page.content: To write this page we had to interview Mr,Burnett and Mr,Brown. Mr,Burnett and Mr,Brown are former members of Gweek Sports Club.Mr Burnett is the Vice Chairman and Mr Brown is the Secretary at the moment. Every month the commitee,which is made up of the President,Vice President,Chairman,Vice Chairman,Secretary,Entertainment Secretary,Treasurer and the Bar Commitee meet. Before the club was built the football team played at a local farm in two of the farmers fields. In exchange they did odd jobs for the farmer during the week like moving bails of straw.
